      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHE'S A SHOW (2) goes very well at the distance with two wins and a placing from six starts. Missed the frame latest (19.89) when fifth over 352m at this track in a Grade 5. Looks suited and should go close. JACK'S THING (5) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (19.80) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Was a winner at her only start from this draw. Expected to feature again. UNPAID DEBT (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Spring Misty (19.99) in a Grade 5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Hard to beat again. MICKEY WILL (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
